flowchart LR
    P[Proposed] --> E[Experimental]
    E --> V[Validated]
    V --> O[Operational]
    O --> D[Deprecated]
    D --> R[Retired]

    E -->|insufficient validity| R
    V -->|workflow or source change| E
    O -->|definition revision| E

    Q[Decision relevance, validity, reliability, quality, and ownership] -. review .-> E
    Q -. review .-> V
    Q -. review .-> O
